title: ASA 5000 software Dec 2013
description:
Just some random ASA 5500 software i found online.
I cant really tell what this software does exactly, but it includes the following:
Cisco ASA 5500 Series images
Cisco ASA 5500-X Series images
Cisco Nexus 1000V virtual appliance image
Active Directory Agent
AnyConnect software
ASDM images
ASDM-IDM Launcher software with demo for Device Manager
Cisco Context Directory Agent
Cisco ASA 5540 8.2(1) Keymaker v1.0 (Sep 2009) by SSG - keymaker to generate SecurityPlus license keys for ASA firewalls.

Please provide comments to help others make more sense of this torrent.
